<div>
<h1>Welcome to Xgrid</h1>
<p>
XGrid is an internal tool developed to ease the deployment of tools in the cloud.
</p>
<p>
It is used to setup Hadoop, SGE or manband workflows environments and can be extended with plugins to get more.
</p>
<br/>
<form action="<%= settings.baseurl %>/login" method="post">
<table class="tabids">
<caption>Enter your Xgrid credentials</caption>
<tr>
<td>
<label for="login">Login</label>
</td>
<td>
<input type="text" id="login" name="login" value="admin"></input>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>
<label for="password">Password</label>
</td>
<td>
<input type="password" id="password" name="password"></input>
<tr>
<td colspan="2">
<input type="submit"></input>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
</form>
</div>
<div class="info">Generated <b>admin</b> password can be found inside the <b>/root/admin_pwd</b> file</div>
